name: Faded Memories [Part Four]
description:
About this series // I start my NFT journey with this genesis piece. This series tells the story of my photography genesis, as this feels right to me. These animated images tell the story of my first exploration adventure, revisiting the now-abandoned theme park I used to love as a child.

Part 4 of 7 // This ride was not here when I was a child. This one is called Knightmare. I remember the Tower of Terror stood here when I used to come here. A rollercoaster that looped around a faux castle, with a hidden loop-the-loop inside. The first time I ever went upside down on a rollercoaster (not knowing this was going to happen when I started the ride!)

Mp4 | 1080x1080 pixels| July  2021
